                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Welcome to the Consumer Goods&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;As Admin: Set Time Zone&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Set the app to the same time zone as your devices.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(60, 64, 67);&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;In Setup, select &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Users,&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; and then edit your user. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;In the Locale Settings section, select the time zone that you’ve set for your devices. Or, go to your profile, click &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Settings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Language &amp;amp; Time Zone&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, and then select the time zone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Install the Consumer Goods Cloud Offline Mobile App&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Download the Consumer Goods Cloud app from&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://apps.apple.com/us/app/consumer-goods-cloud/id1585182357&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;App Store&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;if you’ve an iOS device and from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.salesforce.industries.offlineapp&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Google Play Store&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;if you’ve an Android device.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;Start the App and Log In to the Offline Mobile App&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;To login in the mobile app quickly, in Setup, select &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Users&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, search for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Chantelle&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, edit this user, go to the Local Settings section, update Locale as &quot;English (US)&quot; and Language as &quot;English&quot;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(29, 28, 29); background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);&quot;&gt;Copy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; the Username of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Chantelle&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. Enter the saved Username and Password as &quot;Test12345a&quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
